videos.headline: Liberty's Hickson breaks out for 66-yard TD
videos.description: Frankie Hickson gives the Liberty a 14-7 lead over Louisiana after breaking out for a 66-yard touchdown run in the 2nd quarter.

videos.headline: Louisiana's Lewis connects with Bradley for 58-yard Louisiana TD
